{"tid":1066732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超護級討論區 2018/19","createTime":"2019-03-18T05:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T22:54:52.000Z","uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf80617d99449251f050a4bf8de5fe85ac46d29","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"富咸同哈多士應該降班<br />\n唔講了<br />\n<br />\n護級形勢：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NY1nLqj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNY1nLqj.png&h=834568b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家講最大機會降班的卡迪夫城<br />\n護級大戰：<span style=\"color: red;\">般尼、富咸</span><br />\n仍需搶分護級的球隊：<span style=\"color: teal;\">水晶宮、白禮頓</span><br />\n對Big6大戰：<span style=\"color: blue;\">獌、車、利、鏝</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nubfkYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnubfkYb.png&h=d18ea878&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NRi3bx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NRi3bx.png&h=2cacf20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：卡迪夫城8場都係硬仗<br />\n降班機會大於90%<br />\n<br />\n等陣分析埋般尼同修咸頓"},{"pid":"a9a7465404dc71d133e716fd81ee78235cd1cae7","tid":1066732,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"原來咁多隊未reach到40分安全線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0944cd9c4bb77e877cdab9dcacd890fffcb70783","tid":1066732,"uid":11270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"其實都無咩野有得討論,卡迪夫城雖然分數上唔差得太多但賽程太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 4場護級大戰仲要係1主3客<br />\n拎唔拎到兩場贏仗都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970c0a6ea4ba75fff55fa3e2a0ecdd5ea88e5eea","tid":1066732,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"今季護級無上幾季刺激<br />\n主要係最後兩隊廢過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41154923b3e04cd2e5ea597bca67d017cdf9960e","tid":1066732,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a7465404dc71d133e716fd81ee78235cd1cae7","tid":1066732,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"原來咁多隊未reach到40分安全線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"今季大部分應該35都安全啦"},{"pid":"cf3852c80525097e2ad916a016e7c940f64fa0d0","tid":1066732,"uid":11270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"970c0a6ea4ba75fff55fa3e2a0ecdd5ea88e5eea","tid":1066732,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"今季護級無上幾季刺激<br />\n主要係最後兩隊廢過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"上兩季都唔算叫刺激,未完季已經分出勝負<br />\n對上一次有survival sunday好似已經幾年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e06a6d820678f4b497f6811ca723ef971b633d","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"既然係咁有無人想睇埋修咸頓同般尼？"},{"pid":"9a0e8dfd9d03f636d7352b95a2f06db884540826","tid":1066732,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"米玩啦富咸點拎14分呀？(笑咸emoji)"},{"pid":"1dc1b12e66ff9776453e4d4cf7a7551e6b9aa5be","tid":1066732,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3e06a6d820678f4b497f6811ca723ef971b633d","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"既然係咁有無人想睇埋修咸頓同般尼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"修頓賽程太好啦,唔計其餘6場本身都揸住兩場主場對風流隊既比賽<br />\n贏曬拎到6分都應該夠<br />\n<br />\n般尼其實賽程都差但揸住場對卡城既主場比賽,一贏咗就完季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以如果想刺激D唯有支持卡城贏般尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果對完呢場卡城有分數上既優勢就變咗般尼9成要降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />般尼剩返4場有3場對big 6 1場作客拖肥"},{"pid":"095016b89b21aaba2e35d07205732743c8b807ff","tid":1066732,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:39:37.000Z","msg":"卡迪夫個賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522b6f85b4cb29ec760eb9646c0abdaed58afa11","tid":1066732,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"般尼下場主場對狼隊其實好大機會拎曬3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狼隊今季對中下游成績好差,哈多士都雙炒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過般尼近況都好差,早兩日果場對李城班英冠神鋒既埋門能力真係差到得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad7847df2c6f8293e2d24e57ac87f72ba8b8c16","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LW6ySuh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLW6ySuh.png&h=a2f4147e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUmKY9h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUmKY9h.png&h=7deaa4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n風流波：狼隊、般尼茅夫、愛華頓<br />\n護級大戰：卡迪夫<br />\nbig6大戰：車、鏝、阿<br />\n<br />\n般尼雖然多打一場，但由於狼隊入左FA Cup四強<br />\n應該會留力（6日後踢四強）<br />\n而般尼茅夫等收工，贏既機會都唔細<br />\n愛華頓可能會盡力爭前7，但到時37輪可能乜都無得爭，要再觀望一下<br />\n<br />\n總結：般尼只要唔輸卡迪夫城，應該會夠分護級成功"},{"pid":"34f27505b355768ba57e71d21b8107b87b69cb85","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"修咸頓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eaZgQh4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaZgQh4.png&h=ec71fcc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWPAmpK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWPAmpK.png&h=6e513f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n護級大戰：白禮頓<br />\nBig6大戰：修咸頓B隊利物浦<br />\n風流波：屈福特、狼隊、紐卡素、般尼茅夫、韋斯咸、哈多士<br />\n<br />\n修咸頓係護級形勢最有利既一隊<br />\n佢地唔單止有得對等降班既哈多士，而且Big6只需要對利物浦，所以佢地只要唔太柒都足夠護級"},{"pid":"dd669ceeb29252a100f1a2b7c895b17f25fea34d","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9a0e8dfd9d03f636d7352b95a2f06db884540826","tid":1066732,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"米玩啦富咸點拎14分呀？(笑咸emoji)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"富咸唔分析了，佢地唔降班我切jer"},{"pid":"f05330030377f42fb563b7f5ee6c40f6886c6056","tid":1066732,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"修咸頓真係好鬼死好命<br />\n上季明明死左七八成<br />\n結果史雲斯臨尾十場自爆輸晒咁濟而無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今季就賽程更加安全"},{"pid":"223114ccea0133210edf429e0b080b42eb5615ce","tid":1066732,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd669ceeb29252a100f1a2b7c895b17f25fea34d","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9a0e8dfd9d03f636d7352b95a2f06db884540826","tid":1066732,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"米玩啦富咸點拎14分呀？(笑咸emoji)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"富咸唔分析了，佢地唔降班我切jer"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"唔計扣過分既樸茅,同期成績黎講哈多士係英超史上第3差,富咸排第5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fefd1cdcc427102078f3e4d417cf332d21ca518","tid":1066732,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f05330030377f42fb563b7f5ee6c40f6886c6056","tid":1066732,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"修咸頓真係好鬼死好命<br